'''LG Wing'''是[[LG电子|LG电子]]生产的一款基于[[安卓系统|安卓系统]]的[[智能手机|智能手机]]，采用旋转式设计，可以将主屏呈T型并露出一个较小的副屏，<ref>{{Cite web|title=LG Wing hands-on: Here's what it's like to actually use the weird swiveling phone|url=https://www.cnet.com/news/lg-wing-price-verizon-hands-on-swiveling-dual-screen-phone-double-flip/|accessdate=2021-03-07|last=La|first=Lynn|work=CNET|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210313025238/https://www.cnet.com/news/lg-wing-price-verizon-hands-on-swiveling-dual-screen-phone-double-flip/|archivedate=2021-03-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>于2020年9月14日在[[韩国|韩国]]发布。<ref>{{Cite web|title=LG Wing release date, price, availability, specifications and features|url=https://www.republicworld.com/technology-news/mobile/lg-wing-release-date-price-specs-and-features.html|accessdate=2021-03-08|last=World|first=Republic|work=Republic World|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210313025729/https://www.republicworld.com/technology-news/mobile/lg-wing-release-date-price-specs-and-features.html|archivedate=2021-03-13|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":6">{{Cite web|title=LG Wing 5G review|url=https://www.techradar.com/reviews/lg-wing-5g-review|accessdate=2021-03-07|last=November 2020|first=David Lumb 01|work=TechRadar|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203104527/https://www.techradar.com/reviews/lg-wing-5g-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>该手机还是LG最新公布的Explorer Project系列的第一台设备。<ref>{{Cite web|title=LG teases an ‘Explorer Project’ phone with a slide-out display|url=https://www.engadget.com/lg-explorer-project-phone-slide-out-display-093437774.html|accessdate=2021-03-09|work=Engadget|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110042016/https://www.engadget.com/lg-explorer-project-phone-slide-out-display-093437774.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=LG teases an extendable slide-out display for its next Explorer Project phone|url=https://www.theverge.com/2020/9/14/21436954/lg-extendable-sliding-phone-teaser-explorer-project-wing-mobile|accessdate=2021-03-09|date=2020-09-14|last=Gartenberg|first=Chaim|work=The Verge|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308185011/https://www.theverge.com/2020/9/14/21436954/lg-extendable-sliding-phone-teaser-explorer-project-wing-mobile/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 设计 ==

LG Wing主屏幕搭载6.8英寸[[OLED|OLED]]屏幕，分辨率为2460 × 1080。副屏则采用3.9英寸[[OLED|OLED]]屏幕，分辨率为1240 × 1080。

LG Wing主屏幕采用屏下指纹解锁，可将主屏幕顺时针90度<ref>{{Cite web|title=LG Wing LG Wing smartphone flies high with a crazy rotating screen|url=https://www.digitaltrends.com/mobile/lg-wing-news/|accessdate=2021-03-07|work=www.digitaltrends.com|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116183152/https://www.digitaltrends.com/mobile/lg-wing-news/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，手机内有铰链设计，并安装了[[阻尼器|液压阻尼器]]减少手机旋转时的摩擦<ref>{{Cite web|title=LG WING獨創旋轉雙螢幕限量僅千台12／1正式上市 - 科技|url=https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201126003274-260412?chdtv|access-date=2021-10-15|last=中時新聞網|work=中時新聞網|language=zh-TW}}</ref>。边框采用[[阳极处理|阳极氧化铝]]材质，羽翼蓝的后盖采用炫彩玻璃设计，在阳光下会反射多种色彩。机身通过{{link-en|MIL-STD 810G测试|MIL-STD 810G}}，屏幕表面还涂有[[印刷電路板|PCB]]防水涂层， 防水等级为[[国际防护等级认证|IP54]]。<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=探索新出路 旋轉雙螢幕手機LG WING激發擁有慾|url=https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201216000009-260412?chdtv|accessdate=2021-03-08|last=中時新聞網|work=中時新聞網|language=zh-TW}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=LG Wing 是一款看起来怪，但用起来顺的双屏手机|url=http://cn.engadget.com/lg-wing-5g-preview-hands-on-swivel-screen-141453172.html|accessdate=2021-03-07|work=Engadget 中国版|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120130957/https://cn.engadget.com/lg-wing-5g-preview-hands-on-swivel-screen-141453172.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

可旋转的主屏幕后面有一层热塑性[[聚甲醛|聚甲醛]]涂层，让屏幕旋转更加顺滑，同时避免副屏幕被刮花。LG官方测试大约可旋转20W次，还附赠2年保修。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=LG Wing release date, price, specs and what the dual screens do|url=https://www.tomsguide.com/news/lg-wing-revealed-meet-the-weirdest-phone-of-2020|accessdate=2021-03-07|last=September 2020|first=Adam Ismail 29|work=Tom's Guide|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030101115/https://www.tomsguide.com/news/lg-wing-revealed-meet-the-weirdest-phone-of-2020|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=LG WING, Official Site, LMF100N|url=https://www.lg.com/global/lgwing|accessdate=2021-03-08|work=LG USA|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211175435/https://www.lg.com/global/lgwing|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 摄像 ==
=== 前置相机 ===

前置使用3200W弹出式升降镜头，机身内置[[陀螺仪|陀螺仪]]可检测手机是否掉落，会根据环境变化自动将镜头缩回。<ref>{{Cite web|title=INSIDE THE ONE-AND-ONLY LG WING {{!}} LG NEWSROOM|url=https://www.lgnewsroom.com/2020/11/inside-the-one-and-only-lg-wing/|accessdate=2021-03-08|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130170817/http://lgnewsroom.com/2020/11/inside-the-one-and-only-lg-wing/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=LG Wing smartphone has a swivel screen|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/technology-54146125|newspaper=BBC News|date=2020-09-14|accessdate=2021-03-08|language=en-GB|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021144752/https://www.bbc.com/news/technology-54146125|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 后置相机 ===

后置采用6400W主摄、1300W超广角、1200W微云台运动镜头三镜头矩形排列。<ref name=":3">{{Cite web|title=The LG Wing's Swiveling Screen Proves Phones Can Be Fun Again|url=https://www.wired.com/review/lg-wing/|accessdate=2021-03-08|last=Nast|first=Condé|work=Wired|language=en-us|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125141947/https://www.wired.com/review/lg-wing/|dead-url=no}}</ref>1200W微云台运动相机镜头加上稳定器模式，这是全球第二台采用这种设计的智能手机设备，第一台是[[Vivo_X50|Vivo X50 Pro]]。<ref name=":0" />

== 性能与体验 ==

LG Wing搭载了[[高通骁龙|高通骁龙765G]]，该芯片以三星7[[納米|nm]][[极紫外光刻|EUV]]工艺打造，拥有[[ARM_Cortex-A76|ARM Cortex-A76]]和[[ARM_Cortex-A55|ARM Cortex-A55]]的8核CPU与Adreno 620[[GPU|GPU]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Snapdragon 765G 5G Mobile Platform|url=https://www.qualcomm.com/products/snapdragon-765g-5g-mobile-platform|accessdate=2021-03-07|date=2019-11-22|work=Qualcomm|language=en|archive-date=2019-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191204201734/https://www.qualcomm.com/products/snapdragon-765g-5g-mobile-platform|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=LG WING 5G Mobile Phone Price and Specifications|url=https://www.lg.com/in/mobile-phones/lg-lmf100emw|accessdate=2021-03-07|work=LG India|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204053645/https://www.lg.com/in/mobile-phones/lg-lmf100emw|dead-url=no}}</ref>

LG WING在[[安兔兔|安兔兔]]测试为329192分，[[Geekbench|Geekbench 5]]单核心测试为614分、多核心测试1908分，稍微高于同处理器的[[Google_Pixel_4a_5G|Google Pixel 4a 5G]]、[[Google_Pixel_5|Google Pixel 5]]（283451，584/1608；211295，594/1615）。<ref name=":1" />

== 软件 ==

日常使用时，6.8[[英寸|英寸]]主屏处于Basic模式。若有多屏操作的需求，可将主屏顺时针旋转90度切换旋转模式（Swivel），与3.9[[英寸|英寸]]副屏搭配使用。<ref>{{Cite web|title=LG Wing review: A small extra screen that adds huge value|url=https://indianexpress.com/article/technology/tech-reviews/lg-wing-review-a-small-extra-screen-that-adds-huge-value-7139545/|accessdate=2021-03-08|date=2021-01-10|work=The Indian Express|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117070937/https://indianexpress.com/article/technology/tech-reviews/lg-wing-review-a-small-extra-screen-that-adds-huge-value-7139545/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

LG Wing支持触控笔使用，与{{tsl|en|LG V60 ThinQ||LG V60 ThinQ}}触控笔体验大致相同。<ref name=":4">{{Cite web|title=LG Wing 5G review: Novel dual screen approach, limited productivity use cases Review|url=https://www.zdnet.com/product/lg-wing/|accessdate=2021-03-08|work=ZDNet|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127160304/https://www.zdnet.com/product/lg-wing/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 配件 ==

LG提供的原厂保护壳只能包裹住机身主体，可旋转的主屏无法保护。[[engadget|engadget]]在测试过程中不小心将处于合着状态的手机摔落，屏幕顶角和听筒旁边出现划痕。他们猜测屏幕如果处于展开状态摔落地下，后果会比合着状态更加严重。<ref name=":2" />

